This paper deals with the topics of machine learning models, adversarial attacks, and backdoors. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the security aspect of machine learning models, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Additionally, the paper uses deep neural networks for its experiments, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper also discusses the optimization of machine learning models, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
